elog - simple event log
-----------------------

elog is a simple program that can add enteries with an optonal
message. It can report time elapsed since the last entry in that file.

Every entry consists of the time and date on one line, and an indented
messege on the next line.

[options]
elog has three options: add, time, show

add option will register the current time and date is a new entry
and the messege for that entry if the user wants.

time option will print the time since the last entry.

show option will open the event log file.

[event log file]
The event log file's default location is XDG_CONFIG_HOME/event_log.
if EVENT_LOG variable is set, it will be used instead.
